{"word":"γεγωνέω","slug":"γεγωνέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>γεγωνέω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>formed from <a href='S:γέγωνα'><el>γέγωνα</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b>used in same sense as <el>γέγωνα</el>,<b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> rei, <i>to tell out, proclaim</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}